HEADWORD: Blast pipe
<hw>Blast" pipe`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <def>The exhaust pipe of a steam
engine, or any pipe delivering steam or air, when so constructed as to
cause a blast.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Blastula</ent>⟦br⟧
